<p>A pair of fulltime, single-purpose-account, spamfighters keep trying to delete this popular article. Is there some kind of policy against this type of tagteam disruption? </p>
<p>How many attempts are allowed at deletion? Both regular deletion attempts and backdoor attempts? There have been 4 AfDs already. </p>
<p>I happen to have this article on my watchlist, and these guys are relentless. I didn&#39;t create this chart, and I don&#39;t have infinite patience, so if people want more than a token list of wiki farms, then others will have to step in. --<a href="" title="User:Timeshifter"><b>Timeshifter</b></a> (<a href="" title="User talk:Timeshifter">talk</a>) 10:08, 5 June 2009 (UTC)
